'''''Batman: Arkham Unhinged''''' is an [[American comic book]] series published by [[DC Comics]]. Like the previous anthology, ''[[Batman: Arkham City (comic book)|Batman: Arkham City]]'', it acts as a prequel to the events of the video game ''[[Batman: Arkham City]]''.
== Synopsis == Issues 1-43 were written by [[Derek Fridolfs]]; Issues 44-58 by [[Karen Traviss]].
